Anteater Chess
A fun variation of chess on a 8 x 10 board which introduces a new piece, the Anteater, which fundamentally changes how traditional chess is played with its unique moveset of eating consequtive pawns in a row.
Test your skills against three varying difficulties of bots or play against your friends.

